com.nokia.mid.ui
Interface PopupListListener

public interface PopupListListener

This interface should be implemented by anyone who wishes to receive events from a PopupList. It enables the list instances to call back to their owner with UI event information. When the user dismisses a PopupList it is automatically set as visible false

Method Summary

          This function is implemented to receive a callback when a list item is selected.

Parameters:

item - The instance of the PopupListItem that was selected.

listDismissed

void listDismissed(PopupList list)
This function is implemented to receive a callback when a list is dismissed. (eg. When the user taps outside the list, the owner is notified.)

Parameters:
list - The instance of the PopupList that generated the event.
